attributes.title: Do not download!
attributes.review: This app took hours on end to download and I couldn't do anything while it downloaded. Once I opened the app, a horrid smell came from my phone and attracted many cockroaches and large rats. After a few minutes of me trying to figure out that the smell came from the app, a sound that literally ruptured my ear drums killed all of those roaches and rats. Then not long after, a blond, overly-tanned man crawled through my speaker and slapped my baby brother and then drop-kicked my puppy. He then grabbed a fish out of our fish tank and fried it to make a fish filet for himself. I do not recommend this app at all because of how awful it is.

attributes.title: This app deserves to be deleted
attributes.review: It took me five hours to download on my iPhone with perfectly good wifi. When I finally opened it and tried to open the app it was super glitchy and crashed my device. This app also drained my battery while it was opened. I 100% do NOT recommend you download this app. It crashed my phone multiple times and was really low quality over all. One star.
